  "intro_html": "<b>Just talk — I'll do it.</b> Tell me what you want and ANIMA <b>operates the sheet</b> for you: “<b>sort by revenue and highlight the top 5</b>”, “<b>build a January expenses table</b>”, “<b>sum column B and add totals</b>”. Every number is <b>recomputed and verified</b> by the engine.<br>Offline knowledge: the <code>=ANIMA(\"…\")</code> formula answers from the <b>device's brain</b> (e.g. <code>=ANIMA(\"capital of France\")</code>) or “add the capital of each country in column A”.<br><span style=\"color:var(--muted)\">No forced formulas — talk in English or Italian.</span>",

